===Etymology===
The word "stationery," refering to paper goods was originally spelled as "stationary". This was due to the fact that such goods were sold in "stationary" shops and not from travelling peddlers. Frequency data indicates that "stationary" is preferred to "stationery" for the spelling.  See [http://stationary.name Stationary Nation]


